Package ioio.lib.util

Interface Summary
IOIOLooper A handler implementing interaction with a single IOIO over a single connection period.
IOIOLooperProvider An entity that provides IOIOLooper instances on demand, per connection specifications.
 

Class Summary
AbstractIOIOActivity Deprecated. Please use IOIOActivity instead.
BaseIOIOLooper A convenience implementation of IOIOLooper.
IOIOApplicationHelper A helper class for creating different kinds of IOIO based applications.
IOIOConnectionRegistry A utility class for managing available connection types to IOIO.
